  <version>1.1.6.RELEASE</version>

  <name>OpenEngSB :: Core :: Common </name>

  <packaging>bundle</packaging>

  <description>
    OpenEngSB Common Core Utility classes, abstract classes to be extended by Domains and Connectors
    (Domains, DomainEvents, DomainProviders, ServiceManagers), interfaces to be implemented by Domains,
    Connectors and Events which handle intatiation of Services and Proxies, classes for registration
    of bundles and services, classes for localization, classes that save connector properties (Persistence)
    and finally classes that enable the web application to have access to OSGI bundles.
  </description>
